ed="T" n="0818c14"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0818c14"/><head><date from-iso="+0951-02-18" key="j20684542071729" to-iso="+0960-02-06">周</date><placeName key="PL000000023665"><placeName>洛京</placeName><placeName>福先寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011683">道丕</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0818c15"/><persName key="A011683">釋道丕</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000042096"><placeName>長安</placeName><placeName>貴胄里</placeName></placeName>人也。<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName>之宗室，父<persName key="A011970">從晏</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0818c16"/><persName key="A003875">襄宗</persName>沿堂五院之首<ptr target="#n2271"/>。母<persName key="A019424">許<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>為求其息，常<lb
ed="T" n="0818c17"/>持《觀音普門品》<ptr target="#n1187"/>，忽夢神光燭身，因爾妊焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0818c18"/>及其誕生，挺然岐嶷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1447"/>，端雅其質，<anchor xml:id="beg0818sgsz11"/>屬籍<anchor xml:id="end0818sgsz11"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1157"/>諸親異<lb
ed="T" n="0818c19"/>而愛之如天童子。<date key="j20461552046538" from-iso="+0890-01-29" to-iso="+0891-02-16">年始周晬</date>，父將命<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1158"/><placeName key="PL000000003819">汾晉</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0818c20"/>會軍至于<placeName key="PL000000005675">霍山</placeName>，沒王事。<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>雖童穉聚戲，終<lb
ed="T" n="0818c21"/>鮮笑容。<date key="j20479862048339" from-iso="+0895-02-03" to-iso="+0896-01-22">七歲</date>，忽絕葷羶，每遊精舍，怡然忘<lb
ed="T" n="0818c22"/>返。遂白<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>往<placeName key="PL000000042165">保壽寺</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0818sgsz13"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0818sgsz13"/><persName key="A011971">繼能<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>，尊為軌<lb
ed="T" n="0818c23"/>範。<date key="j20487242049077" from-iso="+0897-02-10" to-iso="+0898-01-29">九歲</date>，善<name>梵</name>音<anchor xml:id="beg0818sgsz15"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0818sgsz15"/>讚。是歲<persName key="A003875">襄宗</persName>幸<placeName key="PL000000058296">石門</placeName>，隨<lb
ed="T" n="0818c24"/><ref type="person" target="#A011971">師</ref>往迎駕。<date key="j20523852052739" from-iso="+0907-02-20" to-iso="+0908-02-09">十九歲</date>，學通《金剛經》義，便行講<lb
ed="T" n="0818c25"/>貫。又<ref type="person" target="#A006572">駕</ref>遷<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛京</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>焚蕩<ptr target="#n2273"/>，遂背負其<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>，東<lb
ed="T" n="0818c26"/>征<placeName key="PL000000043552">華陰</placeName>。<persName key="A011974">劉開道</persName>作亂，復荷<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>入<placeName key="PL000000043539">華山</placeName>，安止<lb
ed="T" n="0818c27"/>巖穴。時穀麥勇貴，每斗萬錢。<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>巡村乞食，<lb
ed="T" n="0818c28"/>自專胎息<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1159"/>，唯供<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>食。<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>問：「還食未？」<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>對曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0818c29"/>「向外齋了。」恐傷<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>意，至孝如此。<date key="j20527402053094" from-iso="+0908-02-10" to-iso="+0909-01-29">年二十歲</date>，<pb ed="T" n="0819a" xml:id="T50.2061.0819a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0819a01"/><ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A011970">汝父</ref><placeName key="PL000000005675">霍山</placeName>亡沒，戰場之地，骨曝霜露。<lb
ed="T" n="0819a02"/><ref type="person" target="#A011683">汝</ref>能收取歸葬，不亦孝乎？」遂辭老親往<placeName key="PL000000005675">霍<lb
ed="T" n="0819a03"/>邑</placeName>，立草庵，鳩工集聚白骨，晝夜誦經，呪<lb
ed="T" n="0819a04"/>之曰：「古人精誠所感，滴血認骨。<ref type="person" target="#A011683">我</ref>今志為<lb
ed="T" n="0819a05"/>孝子，豈無靈驗者乎？儻群骨中有動轉者，<lb
ed="T" n="0819a06"/>即<ref type="person" target="#A011970">我父</ref>之遺骸也。」如是一心注想，目未輕捨，<lb
ed="T" n="0819a07"/>數日間，果有枯髏從骨聚中躍出，競騖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g957"/><persName key="A011683">丕</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0819a08"/>前，搖曳良久<ptr target="#n2838"/>。<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>即<anchor xml:id="beg0819001"/>躄<anchor xml:id="end0819001"/>踴抱持，如復生在，齎<lb
ed="T" n="0819a09"/>歸<placeName key="PL000000043552">華陰</placeName>。是夜其<ref type="person" target="#A019424">母</ref>夢<ref type="person" target="#A011970">夫</ref>歸舍，明辰骨至，其<lb
ed="T" n="0819a10"/>孝感聲譽日高。至<date key="j20552792055662" from-iso="+0915-01-23" to-iso="+0916-02-10">二十七歲</date>，遇<placeName key="PL000000042732">曜州</placeName>牧<persName key="A011975">婁繼<lb
ed="T" n="0819a11"/>英</persName>，招<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>住<placeName key="PL000000058305"><placeName>洛陽</placeName><placeName>福先</placeName><placeName>彌勒院</placeName></placeName>，即<placeName key="PL000000000103">晉</placeName><persName key="A001503">道安</persName><placeName key="PL000000023666">翻經</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0819a12"/>創<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz1"/>浴<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz1"/>之地也<ptr target="#n2839"/>。<date from-iso="+0906-02-02" key="j20520022052384" to-iso="+0907-02-19"><name>天祐</name>三年丙寅</date>，<persName key="A006572">濟陰王</persName>賜紫衣。<lb
ed="T" n="0819a13"/><placeName key="PL000000057656">後唐</placeName><persName key="A006575">莊宗</persName>署大師曰<persName key="A011683">廣智</persName>。<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000048181">梁</placeName>朝<persName key="A006574">後主</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0819a14"/><placeName key="PL000000057656">後唐</placeName><persName key="A006575">莊宗</persName>、<persName key="A006576">明宗</persName>、凡內建香壇，應制談論，多居<lb
ed="T" n="0819a15"/>元席。及<placeName key="PL000000000124">晉</placeName>遷都今<placeName key="PL000000023467">東京</placeName>，<date from-iso="+0938-02-07" key="j20636952064049" to-iso="+0939-01-27"><name>天福</name>三年</date>詔入<placeName key="PL000000023340">梁<lb
ed="T" n="0819a16"/>苑</placeName>，副錄左街僧事，與傳法阿闍梨<persName key="A013628">昭信</persName>大師<lb
ed="T" n="0819a17"/>俱道貌童顏，號<persName key="G000030">二菩薩</persName>。是故朝貴士庶，多請<lb
ed="T" n="0819a18"/>養生之術。<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>精勤不懈，一佛一<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz2"/>。《佛名經》<ptr target="#n1001"/>、《法<lb
ed="T" n="0819a19"/>華》、《金剛》、《仁王》<ptr target="#n198"/>、《上生》<ptr target="#n772"/>四經，逐一字<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz3"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz3"/>。然其守杜<lb
ed="T" n="0819a20"/>多<ptr type="glossary" target="#g566"/>之行，分衛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g602"/>時至，二弟子隨行。<date from-iso="+0944-02-02" key="j20658812066264" to-iso="+0945-02-19"><name>開運</name>甲辰歲</date><lb
ed="T" n="0819a21"/>為左街僧錄，雖臨僧務，日課修持。相國<persName key="A011979">李<lb
ed="T" n="0819a22"/><roleName>公</roleName>濤</persName>、西樞密太傅<persName key="A010031">王<roleName>公</roleName>朴</persName>、翰林<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz5"/>承<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz5"/>旨<persName key="A011980">陶<roleName>公</roleName>穀</persName>等，<lb
ed="T" n="0819a23"/>無不<anchor xml:id="beg0819002"/>傾<anchor xml:id="end0819002"/>心歸重。至<placeName key="PL000000057659">漢</placeName><date notBefore-iso="+0948-02-18" key="j20673582068453" notAfter-iso="+0951-02-17"><name>乾祐</name>中</date>，謝病乞西<lb
ed="T" n="0819a24"/>歸。未允之際，屬<placeName key="PL000000057659">漢</placeName>室凌夷，兵火連作，恣行<lb
ed="T" n="0819a25"/>剽掠<ptr target="#n2274"/>。<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>於廊廡之下，倚壁誦念，二日紛拏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g982"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0819a26"/>一無見者。時<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023327">京城</ref>見聞，益加欽尚。逃歸<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛<lb
ed="T" n="0819a27"/>邑</placeName>，<persName key="A006584">周太祖</persName>潛隱所重。<date from-iso="+0951-02-18" key="j20684542068804" to-iso="+0952-02-03"><name>廣順</name>元年</date>，勅召為左街<lb
ed="T" n="0819a28"/>僧錄，不容陳讓，還赴<placeName key="PL000000023327">東京</placeName>，居于僧任。<persName key="A006586">世宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0819a29"/>尹釐府政<ptr target="#n2275"/>，嫌空門繁雜，欲奏沙汰，召<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>同<pb ed="T" n="0819b" xml:id="T50.2061.0819b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0819b01"/>議。時問難交發，開喻其情，且曰：「僧之清尚，必<lb
ed="T" n="0819b02"/>不露於人前。僧或凶頑，而偏遊於世上。必<lb
ed="T" n="0819b03"/>恐正施藨<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz7"/><g ref="#Z1184"/><anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz7"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1160"/>，草和蘭<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>茞</sic><corr>茝</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz9"/>而芟；方事淘澄，金<lb
ed="T" n="0819b04"/>逐沙泥而蕩。大王儲明欲照，蓄智當行，為<lb
ed="T" n="0819b05"/>益皇帝邪？為損君親邪？若益君乎，不令<lb
ed="T" n="0819b06"/>一物失所。若損親也，是壞六和<ptr type="glossary" target="#g25"/>福田。況以<lb
ed="T" n="0819b07"/>天下初平，瘡痍未合，乞待後時，搜揚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g859"/>未晚。<lb
ed="T" n="0819b08"/>故<persName key="A002104">老子</persName>云：『治大國如<anchor xml:id="beg0819003"/>烹<anchor xml:id="end0819003"/>小鮮。<ptr target="#n969"/>』慮其動則麋<lb
ed="T" n="0819b09"/>爛矣。」<persName key="A006586">世宗</persName>深然其言，且從停寢。及<persName key="A006586">世宗</persName>登<lb
ed="T" n="0819b10"/>極，<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>謂僧曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A006586">吾皇</ref>宿昔有志，汝當相警護<lb
ed="T" n="0819b11"/>持。」堅乞解歸<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛陽</placeName>，又立<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz11"/>《首楞嚴經》<ptr target="#n92"/>。<date from-iso="+0955-02-01" key="j20698982070281" to-iso="+0956-02-19">二年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0819b12"/>果勅併毀僧寺，并立僧帳，蓋限之也<ptr target="#n2276"/>。毀教<lb
ed="T" n="0819b13"/>不深，乃<persName key="A011683">丕</persName>之力也。以<date key="j20700522070052" when-iso="+0955-07-05"><name>顯德</name>二年乙卯六月八<lb
ed="T" n="0819b14"/>日</date>微疾。<date key="j20700542070054" when-iso="+0955-07-07">十日</date>，令弟子早營粥食云：「有首楞<lb
ed="T" n="0819b15"/>嚴菩薩眾多相迎」，令鳴椎，俄然而化，春秋<lb
ed="T" n="0819b16"/>六十七，僧臘四十七。緇素號哭，諸寺具威儀<lb
ed="T" n="0819b17"/>送葬于<placeName key="PL000000023667"><placeName>龍門</placeName><placeName>廣化寺</placeName></placeName>之左，立石塔焉。未終<lb
ed="T" n="0819b18"/>之前，寺鐘無故嘶嗄、表剎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1161"/>龍首忽焉隕墜、僧<lb
ed="T" n="0819b19"/><persName key="A011982">澄清</persName>夢寺佛殿梁折，極多異兆焉。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0819b2001"><lb
ed="T" n="0819b20"/>系曰：<persName key="A004350">周武</persName>滅佛法。<placeName key="PL000000000105">隋</placeName><date from-iso="+0591-02-02" key="j19369511937333" to-iso="+0592-02-19"><name>開皇</name>辛亥歲</date>，太府丞<persName key="A023383">趙<lb
ed="T" n="0819b21"/>文昌</persName>入冥見<persName key="A004350">邕</persName>受對，寄語<persName key="A004324">文帝</persName>拔救<ptr target="#n2277"/>。<persName key="A006586">周世<lb
ed="T" n="0819b22"/>宗</persName>澄汰，毀私邑，勒立僧帳，故說大漸招其惡<lb
ed="T" n="0819b23"/>報<ptr target="#n2278"/>。或有入冥見之，并贊成厥事者，同居負<lb
ed="T" n="0819b24"/>處，略同<persName key="A004350">周武</persName>。未知是乎？</p><milestone unit="page" rend="pagebreak"/>
